desc:
Our CSI Person Reports are not bringing back property details, in this case a search was done on 5410155104082 and result shows that the owner does not own any property, however Deeds Office search shows in fact the individual owns property. Shaun has queried this with data provider and they've advised that the Trace product - BonusXML segment was not passed to their platform for the enquiry made.

They've asked that dev please investigate and confirm if you're adding bonus segments and pass to xds platform to receive the deeds information on Trace report.

I have forwarded the email on to dev for further information should they require this
name: SW - CSI Person Report Property
